General.Name: Sino Geophysical
General.Description: Sino Geophysical Co., Ltd. provides integrated oil and gas exploration and development technology services in China and internationally. The company offers technical services, such as acquisition and processing integration, and unconventional oil and gas, and geothermal services, as well as earthquake, geological, and engineering integration services. It is also involved in the oil and gas investment; and asset management activities. Sino Geophysical Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.
